      <p class="lead">Hey there! I’m Griffen, a user experience designer with a <a href="https://www.sydney.edu.au/courses/courses/uc/bachelor-of-design-computing.html">Bachelor of Design Computing</a> from the University of Sydney. I believe that good design has the power to make the world a better place.</p>
      <p>I’m the former President and Vice President of <a href="https://www.suede.org.au/">Sydney University Experience Designers (SUEDE)</a>, a society driven by students passionate about the design of everyday interactions, services, and experiences. I am the former Marketing Manager at <a href="https://www.canterburytheatreguild.com/">Canterbury Theatre Guild</a>, where I promoted the performing arts to the community. I have contributed to many <a href="https://github.com/griffenedge">GitHub</a> repositories, including <a href="/prioritab/">Prioritab</a> which I redesigned and is now used by over 18,000 users.</p>
      <p>I have always had an interest in design, be it with photography, stage lighting, fashion, interior design or digital media.</p>
